  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0dbd\u0d9a\u0dca\u0dc2 160\u0d9a \u0db8\u0dad\u0dca\u0d9a\u0dd4\u0da9\u0dd4 \u0dc3\u0db8\u0d9c \u0d85\u0db9\u0dd4\u0dc3\u0dd0\u0db8\u0dd2 \u0dba\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dbd\u0d9a\u0dca \u0d85\u0dad\u0dca\u0d85\u0da9\u0d82\u0d9c\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A husband and wife couple arrested with drugs worth 160 lakhs",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to the Criminal Investigation Department of Mount Kilissa, a husband and wife couple was arrested at a house in Atthidiya last night with a stash of drugs worth nearly one crore 60 lakh rupees. The suspect is a labor employee of Dehiwala Mt",
        "The suspect was in possession of 45 grams of drugs and the suspect was in possession of 810 grams of drugs, an electric scale, a spoon used for packing drugs, a sum of Rs. The police have taken over",
        "The raid was carried out according to information received by Sub Inspector Chanaka during a long investigation conducted under the direct supervision of Mt. Chief Inspector Gamage Nilantha, Station Commander of the Mount Kilissa Division Criminal Investigation Division.",
        "At the time of the raid, the husband and wife were packing drugs inside the house, police said",
        "It has been revealed in the long interrogation of the suspected husband and wife that the mistress of Marvin Jana, a major drug trafficker who is currently detained in Bussa prison, Dilini, a resident of Russia, owns the drug stock.",
        "Police say that the arrested suspected husband and wife had been running their house as a drug packing center for several years and the packaged drugs were distributed to areas such as Mt. Piliyandala, Moratuwa, Panadura etc.",
        "A police officer who conducted the raid said that the small-sized stamped paper with the \"Facebook logo\" was used to pack drugs and the arrested suspect couple are between the ages of 35 and 37.",
        "The suspect couple will be presented to the court. On the advice of the Senior Superintendent of Police in charge of Galkissa Division Mr. Mangala Dehideniya, under the direct supervision of Chief Inspector Gamage Nilantha, Station Commander of Galkissa Division Criminal Investigation Division, Sub Inspector Nil, Chanaka, Police Sergeants 8397",
        "Jayawardena 53810 Ajith Police Constables 85557 Weerasinghe 90027 Vitarana, Ladies Police Constable 12995 Shakila Mahatma conducted the raid."
      ],
